content: Today, I am going to introduce very old Japanese tournament.
First, I must tell you the historical issue.
Japanese Meijinsen started 42 years ago, you know?

Did he invent the SAKATA rule? :)
However, after Sakata died, that sponsor  cancelled the support Meijinsen.
Mr. Sakata-Gozui is the 5th forever Meijin. not as Sakata-rule.
He was so strong and loved.
The most important person at renju history.
One of his puple is Mr. Nishimura.
Instead of Meijinsen, top ten league wa s held at first.

But for the renjufan, top ten league was very interesting.
Because including meijin(Mr. Isobe) took part in that tournament.

I5 opening was allowed for the first time.
i hope i can come back to that year
1st time, in 1974, Mr. Isobe won with 9-0 socore!!
hmmmm with I7 or D4 opening?
